org.jasig.cas.authentication.principal

Class BasicPrincipalResolver

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jasig.cas.authentication.principal.BasicPrincipalResolver
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PrincipalResolver

    @Component(value="proxyPrincipalResolver")
public class BasicPrincipalResolver
extends java.lang.Object
implements PrincipalResolver
    Provides the most basic means of principal resolution by mapping Credential.getId() onto Principal.getId().
